  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Who's Who 2.0 is causal, party battle royale genre game which have elevated the fun of the battle to another level. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>You will have to find real players lurking among the NPCs and kick them out of the game with your new skills! find your own psychological and strategical way to be the last man standing!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">✦ A variety of characters & skins ✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/2929874e1f6fbfaa3f91377322dbc91b.poster.avif?t=1773978518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/2929874e1f6fbfaa3f91377322dbc91b.webm?t=1773978518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/2929874e1f6fbfaa3f91377322dbc91b.mp4?t=1773978518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">✦ Skills ✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/a590c20a795c0978b803fac32ef2a010.poster.avif?t=1773978518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/a590c20a795c0978b803fac32ef2a010.webm?t=1773978518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/a590c20a795c0978b803fac32ef2a010.mp4?t=1773978518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/8aa328aa7bcda4ab8b208029b5b6691e.poster.avif?t=1773978518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/8aa328aa7bcda4ab8b208029b5b6691e.webm?t=1773978518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/8aa328aa7bcda4ab8b208029b5b6691e.mp4?t=1773978518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">✦ Constantly updated game modes! ✦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/972e0a4d46ce0005d98c21479d01ba63.avif?t=1773978518\" width=990 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/aec419800a65c340da7401a9225028bc.avif?t=1773978518\" width=990 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/98dcf86955a5667fc781cf7116e8eda0.avif?t=1773978518\" width=990 height=213 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391260/extras/67ddfa6412d0414163b1328d4408ba3c.avif?t=1773978518\" width=660 height=213 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">1. Random</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">2.  Last Man Standing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">3. Team Rumble</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">4. Back to Basic</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">5. Bombs Away</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">6. Coupon Frenzy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">7. Team Coupon Frenzy </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">8. CrossFire\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">9. Red Light / Green Light </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">10. Cops & Robbers </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">11. Random DeathMatch\t</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">⭐ Discover a wide variety of characters, skills, and constantly updated game modes! ⭐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">🫶 Enjoy the fun with your family, friends, coworkers, and even the people you meet by chance. Everyone can join the chaos and laughter!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🫶 Streamers and content creators, we want YOU!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Nightvendors actively collaborates with creators on YouTube and various streaming platforms, and we’re always excited to build amazing partnerships with more people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">We’d love to share your passion and creativity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Feel free to reach out. We’d love to talk about exciting ways we can work together😊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><u>Contact us anytime. We can’t wait to meet you!</u></p>",
